title: Donkey Kicks
description: Donkey kicks works your core and shoulder muscles. Toning your muscles reduce fat and increase muscle strength.

title: Sit-Ups
description: Sit-ups are considered strength training. But for a well-rounded workout session, add some more floor routines for effective loss of weight.

title: Bridge Exercise
description: Bridge Exercises enhances your core stability and targets abdominal muscles and lower back and hip muscles when done correctly.

title: Side Plank Push-Ups
description: Side plank push-ups improve your core muscles. It also initiates the muscles in the chest, shoulders, and back.

title: Planks
description: Planks are a core strength exercise working in three dimensions. It is a workout where your body should maintain a position similar to a push-up.

title: Squat
description: The squat is not only a standalone compound movement, its also the base for strength training, moving your bodyweight, and walking.
